_sText:
If you are Metal Gear fan, you should like this map.
This map is the first place in Metal Gear Solid 1.

-----------------------------------------------------------

Dock A

(CT) Snakes: Sneak and kill all guards.

(T) Guards: Kill the Snakes.

Other Notes: Guards have Famas and Glock.
Snakes have only USP.

Credits:
Map by Scytha
